arsus, are mighty in the </div><div class="t m4b5 x3a h26 yaeb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Scriptures, and these will proclaim with wonderful power the immutability </div><div class="t m24a x3a h26 yaec ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the law of God. The God of Israel will bring this to pass in our day. His </div><div class="t m27c x3a h26 yaed ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">arm is not shortened that it cannot save. As His servants labor in faith for </div><div class="t m62 x3a h26 yaee ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">those who have long been neglected and despised, His salvation will be re-</div><div class="t m159 x3a h26 yaef ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">vealed.&quot;â€”The </div><div class="t m3cf x74 h26 yaef ff7 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Acts of the Apostles, </div><div class="t m124 xbd h26 yac1 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 380, 381. </div><div class="t m2c2 x3a h21 yaf0 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FURTHER STUDY AND MEDITATION: </div><div class="t m3fe x8b h26 yd9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Read </div><div class="t mce xa4 h26 y43d ff7 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Acts of the Apos-</div><div class="t m44f x3a h26 yaf1 ff7 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tles, </div><div class="t m3b5 x6 h26 yaf2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Salvation to the Jews,&quot; pp. 372-382. </div><div class="t m450 x3a h26 yaf3 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: Although Israel&apos;s rejection of the Messiah resulted in the </div><div class="t m4f3 x3a h26 yaf4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">loss of their status as a chosen nation before God, the Lord seeks to lead </div><div class="t m423 x3a h26 yaf5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Jewish people to salvation through Jesus Christ. Those who believe are </div><div class="t m3c4 x3a h26 yaf6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">united with believing Gentiles into one body as spiritual Israel. </div><div class="t m1de x58 h21 yaf7 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">76 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
